text.text: v-text directive — Update the element's text content.

show.text: v-show directive — Toggle the element's visibility based on the truthy-ness of the expression value.

if.text: v-if directive — Conditionally render an element or a template fragment based on the truthy-ness of the expression value.

else.text: v-else directive — Denote the "else block" for `v-if` or a `v-if` / `v-else-if` chain.

else-if.text: v-else-if directive — Denote the "else if block" for `v-if`. Can be chained.

for.text: v-for directive — Render the element or template block multiple times based on the source data.

on.text: v-on directive — Attach an event listener to the element.

bind.text: v-bind directive — Dynamically bind one or more attributes, or a component prop to an expression.

model.text: v-model directive — Create a two-way binding on a form input element or a component.

slot.text: v-slot directive — Denote named slots or scoped slots that expect to receive props.

pre.text: v-pre directive — Skip compilation for this element and all its children.

once.text: v-once directive — Render the element and component once only, and skip future updates.

cloak.text: v-cloak directive — Used to hide un-compiled template until it is ready.
